{
  "texts": [
    "While GenAI offers many benefits, it can pose some new challenges to knowledge transfer.",
    "Depending on how the AI model is initially developed, its knowledge can come from multiple sources within and outside the organization.",
    "Hence, the organization may lose control of what knowledge is transferred to employees.",
    "Whereas in the past, a major challenge of knowledge management was ensuring the maximum transfer of knowledge, with the introduction of GenAI, the challenge has shifted.",
    "Organizations must be cautious about the type and quantity of information that GenAI shares with employees."
  ]
}